Class RecursiveTreeObject<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jfoenix.controls.datamodels.treetable.RecursiveTreeObject<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - is the concrete object of the Tree table

    public class RecursiveTreeObject<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    data model that is used in JFXTreeTableView, it's used to implement the grouping feature.

    Note: the data object used in JFXTreeTableView must extends this class
